<p data-s="dL9GM======">郑栅洁说，本次对话旨在落实两国领导人加强气候变化和绿色转型对话合作重要共识。</p>
<script data-s="dkFGU======" type="text/javascript"> googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('dfp-ad-imu1'); }); </script>
</article>]]></description><guid isPermaLink="false">3961701</guid><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 14:07:22 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>感化院霸凌事件 三人暴打少男逼脱衣舔鞋</title><link>https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/singapore/story20240622-3961813</link><description><![CDATA[<div class="article-banner carousel slide" data-interval="false" data-ride="carousel" data-touch="true" id="carousel-article">
